[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boston wedding postponed after stag-do neck-break

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A firefighter paralysed after a freak stag-do accident in Majorca has been forced to postpone his wedding as a result of his injuries.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
James Thorpe, 28, and Michaela Watson, from Boston, were due to marry this Friday but cancelled the ceremony after Mr Thorpe broke his neck.
He was left paralysed from the chest down after falling in the sea in Magaluf earlier this month
Miss Watson said: "It needs to be perfect and it wouldn't have been".
